premise_source_doc_sentence: Throughout its run , Futurama has received critical acclaim .

It has also been nominated four times for a Writers Guild of America Award , winning two for the episodes `` Godfellas '' and `` The Prisoner of Benda '' , been nominated for a Nebula Award and has received Environmental Media Awards for episodes `` The Problem with Popplers '' and `` The Futurama Holiday Spectacular '' .
Futurama is an American animated science fiction sitcom created by Matt Groening for the Fox Broadcasting Company .
In 2013 , TV Guide ranked Futurama as one of the top 60 Greatest TV Cartoons of All Time .
Futurama also aired in reruns on Cartoon Network 's Adult Swim from 2003 to 2007 , until the network 's contract expired .
